snippet.title: Johnny Depp Funny Moments (Uncensored) #1
snippet.description:
"It's a pirate's life for me, savvy?"💀

From Johnny Depp Best & Funny Moments #7, youtube restricted the video due to some clip with Ricky Gervais so i'm posting the other part here.

THIS IS A SPECIAL GRINDELWALD AND DUMBLEDORE MEMES.

Thank you for watching, sharing and liking if you did so, I deeply appreciate it!
I've spent the last 2 months searching for videos + editing the whole project and now I am DONE. I've worked really really hard on this and tried my very best to deliver my Depphead relatives a HQ content and also to the others who may be able to see thru the lies and  appreciate Johnny Depp for what he TRULY is. 👑

I really hope you enjoyed it and stay tuned because this is only the very first one of a long series! 

→ A HUGE AND SPECIAL THANKS TO ANYONE THAT OWNS SOMETHING IN THIS VIDEO.
THE GIFS FROM THE TUMBLR PEOPLE, THE VIDEOS, THE PHOTOS, THE MUSIC. 🖤✨
